<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <title>Case Report Notification</title>
    <style>
      body { font-family: Arial, sans-serif; background-color: #f4f4f4; margin:
      0; padding: 0; display: flex; justify-content: center; align-items:
      center; height: 100vh; } .container { background-color: #ffffff; padding:
      20px; border-radius: 8px; box-shadow: 0 0 10px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1);
      max-width: 600px; width: 100%; } h1 { color: #333333; } p { color:
      #555555; line-height: 1.6; } a { color: #1a73e8; text-decoration: none; }
      a:hover { text-decoration: underline; }
    </style>
  </head>
  <body>
    <div class="container">
      <h1>Case Report Available</h1>
      <p>Dear {{name}},</p>
      <p>We are pleased to inform you that a report on your case has been
        provided.</p>
      <p>Case Details:</p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Case Name:</strong> {{caseName}}</li>
        <li><strong>Suit No:</strong> {{suitNo}}</li>
        <li><strong>Case Reported:</strong> {{caseReported}}</li>
        <li><strong>Update:</strong> {{update}}</li>
        <li><strong>Adjourned For:</strong> {{adjournedFor}}</li>
        <li><strong>Adjourned Date:</strong> {{adjournedDate}}</li>
        <li><strong>Reported By:</strong> {{reportedBy}}</li>
      </ul>
      <p>You can check the report on your dashboard by clicking the link below:</p>
      <p><a href="{{link}}">View Report</a></p>
      <p>Thank you for your attention.</p>
      <p>Best regards,</p>
      <p>{{companyName}}</p>
      <p>&copy; {{year}} {{companyName}}. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>